<p align="center">本报记者吕甲采访在黑山羊保种繁育基地务工的村民</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201021/c4a7bba5aaf7482f84742ba7a41a2df3.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">耿永涛（左一）与在外务工的村民通话，了解他们的最新情况</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201021/72775eaa6754425a9b7bc15c1a70a7b3.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
